{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"content":["Place lettuce in mixing bowl, cover with 1000 g water and chop <b>2 sec\/speed 4<b>. Drain using simmering basket then transfer to a serving bowl.","Place remaining 500 g water in mixing bowl then insert simmering basket.","Add chicken, lemon juice, 1 tsp salt and chilli powder. Place Varoma dish into position and add eggs. Insert Varoma tray, add potatoes and ½ tsp salt then steam <b>20 min\/Varoma\/speed 2<b>.","Remove Varoma then remove simmering basket with aid of spatula. Cool eggs under cold running water then set aside. Place Varoma back into position and steam potatoes for another <b>5-10 min\/Varoma\/speed 2<b> until cooked. Meanwhile, separate chicken then set aside to cool.","Set Varoma aside and allow potatoes to cool. Meanwhile, clean mixing bowl.","Peel eggs then place in mixing bowl and chop <b>2 sec\/speed 4<b>. Transfer to serving bowl.","Add cooled chicken, cooled potatoes, tomatoes, celery and olives to serving bowl then place in fridge to chill for 30 minutes. Meanwhile, make dressing.","Place mayonnaise, cream and 1 pinch salt in mixing bowl then mix <b>5 sec\/speed 5<b>.","When ready to serve, pour dressing over salad and combine. Sprinkle with chives and serve immediately."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"","content":["6 leaves iceberg lettuce, torn in half (approx. 180 g)","1500 g water","600 g chicken breasts, cut in pieces (2 cm)","1 lemon, juice only (approx. 45 g)","1 ½ tsp fine sea salt, plus 1 pinch","1 pinch chilli powder","4 large eggs","500 g new potatoes, diced, (1 cm)","250 g cherry tomatoes, halved","1 celery stalk, sliced (3 mm)","50 g pitted black olives","150 g mayonnaise","100 g double cream","4 fresh chives, finely snipped"]}],"id":"r123516","imageLink":"https:\/\/2.bp.blogspot.com\/-trcEFyR2Hcw\/XZQumEBQNtI\/AAAAAAAAcVA\/eT7emYN3a2sObcTTj7DlOV0HXEZwzqLCwCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_39uOmGDYAnfnK789.png","title":"Chicken Salad","publishedAt":"2016-08-15T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"36.2 g","fat":"35 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"16.7 g","calories":"2204 kJ \/ 527 kcal"},"usefulItems":"serving bowl, refrigerator","hintsAndTricks":["If potatoes aren't cooked in step 3, remove eggs and chicken then steam again.","Only assemble once chicken and potatoes are cooled and you are ready to serve."],"basicInfo":["easy","20m","1h 20m","6 portions"]}